  "title": "Staff Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide comprehensive nursing care and support to patients</li><li>Assist doctors during consultations and medical procedures</li><li>Administer medications and treatments as prescribed</li><li>Monitor, assess, and record patients’ vital signs and conditions</li><li>Maintain accurate nursing documentation and records</li><li>Ensure patient safety and infection control standards are met</li><li>Assist with patient education and discharge planning</li><li>Perform other nursing duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Nursing</li><li>Valid <strong>SNB Registered</strong></li><li>Prior nursing experience preferred (training provided for junior nurses)</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li>Stable healthcare environment</li><li>Supportive nursing team</li><li>Opportunities for training and career development</li><li>Competitive salary and benefits<br /> <em>(Average 2–3 months AWS + Variable Bonus)</em></li></ul><p>Business Edge Personnel Services Singapore </p><p>EA License No: 96C4864 </p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R26159908 (Tan Ying Ying)</p>",
